title: GCU-12/24
description: Glow Plug Controller / timer. Multi-voltage with crank and temp disable. 4-20 seconds adjustable output

title: GCU-12/24D
description: Glow Plug Controller - Multi-voltage with crank and temp disable - dual relay output. 4-20 seconds adjustable output initial glow, 60 seconds initial second stage output.

title: GCU-12/24P
description: Glow Plug Controller - Multi-voltage with crank and temp disable - pulse relay on afterglow. Our top seller - helps with visible emissions after startup - custom timeframes can be built if desired.

title: 21-5W 3CH
description: Bulb Simulator. Heatsunk & sealed for all weather use. Available in 12V and 24V load to allow OEM electronics to work without faulting when using LEDS in place of bulbs. Suitable for utility flatdeck LED conversions in place of OEM taillights - eg. Amarok & Ranger - loads equivalent to 21w stop & indicator & 5w tail circuits. Requires 2 per vehicle (one per side).

title: 21W2-24
description: Indicator Bulb Simulator. 24V load to simulate filament indicator lamps for LED installations.12V version available on request.

title: HEF-12/24
description: High-Beam Emergency Flasher. Flashes high-beam headlamps in an emergency sequence as required by ambulance & fire service operators.

title: HLW-12/24
description: Headlight Warning Alarm. Triggers an alarm if the ignition is switched off while headlights are on.
